item.title: About me
item.description: Hi everyone, I’m Yiyi Wang, a master student majoring in Language Technology at University of Gothenburg. I’m interested in computer system and natural language processing. I got my B.Eng in Computer Science at School of Computer Science, Wuhan University. Email: guswanyie [AT] student dot gu dot se My GitHub. My Linkdin
